---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="FRM Consulting Group — A technology-driven financial services group delivering holistic client outcomes across Australia, the USA, and the Philippines.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-frm-blue rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-frm-green rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Holistic Financial Services.<br />
          <span class="text-frm-green">Unrelenting Standards.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl">
          FRM Consulting Group is an integrated financial services group that fully and holistically services our clients' needs — from accounting and property to specialised finance and solar energy solutions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/our-companies" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-frm-green text-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-frm-green/90 transition-colors">
            Our Companies
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-400 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:border-white transition-colors">
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Proposition -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-frm-green mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Why an Integrated Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-frm-gray leading-relaxed">
          Most financial service providers operate in silos. Your accountant doesn't talk to your broker. Your property advisor has never met your financial planner. The result is fragmented advice, missed opportunities, and outcomes that fall short of what's possible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-frm-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-frm-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Integrated Services</h3>
          <p class="text-frm-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Our operating companies work together, sharing insights and coordinating strategies so that every decision supports your broader financial position.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-frm-green/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-frm-green-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Client-Centric Outcomes</h3>
          <p class="text-frm-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We exist to deliver outcomes for our clients — not to sell products. Every recommendation is made in the context of your complete financial picture.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-3">International Reach</h3>
          <p class="text-frm-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            FRM Australia is part of an international group with operations in the United States and the Philippines, bringing global perspective to local expertise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-frm-blue mb-6"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Technology-Driven Financial Services</h2>
          <p class="text-frm-gray leading-relaxed mb-4">
            FRM Consulting Group operates across the spectrum of financial services and related industries. We are a technology-driven group that specialises in referral management and delivering coordinated financial outcomes for our clients.
          </p>
          <p class="text-frm-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Through our portfolio of operating companies, we provide accounting, property advisory, specialised lending, renovation finance, and solar finance — all working together under one group to ensure nothing falls through the cracks.
          </p>
          <a href="/executive-team" class="inline-flex items-center text-frm-blue font-medium hover:underline">
            Meet our leadership team
            <svg class="ml-1 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-10 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-frm-green rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy">Accounting & Tax</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-frm-gray">Comprehensive accounting services through Surfside Accounting</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-frm-blue rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy">Property Advisory</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-frm-gray">Wealth creation through property with PMA</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-frm-green-dark rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy">Specialised Finance</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-frm-gray">Tailored lending solutions via SFA</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-navy rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy">Solar & Renovation Finance</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-frm-gray">Purpose-built finance for solar and home renovations</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Work With Us?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Whether you're a potential partner, referrer, or client, we'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-frm-green text-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-frm-green/90 transition-colors">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
